The paper discusses the impact of 5G on IoT platforms, which falls under the category of networked systems and communication (cs.NI). It also covers cloud computing (cs.IT), fog computing (cs.DC), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and software engineering (cs.SE) in relation to IoT and 5G.
